 - alert if last run failed
+
+
+## Rollout gate / manual ack
+
+When the nightly smoke fails, Redis latches a rollout/apply gate and sensitive apply paths are blocked until explicit operator ack.
+
+Check status:
+
+```bash
+python -m orderflow_services.exec_health_freeze_reconnect_rollout_gate_v1 status
+```
+
+Acknowledge after investigation:
+
+```bash
+python -m orderflow_services.exec_health_freeze_reconnect_rollout_gate_v1 ack \
+  --operator alice \
+  --reason "nightly smoke investigated, safe to proceed" \
+  --ticket INC-123
+```
+
+Redis events:
+- ops summary: `ops:exec_health:freeze_events:v1`
+- telegram notify: `notify:telegram`
+- gate key: `cfg:orderflow:exec_health:reconnect_smoke:rollout_gate:v1`
